No. 09-9345. Johnnie Washington, Petitioner v. Harold Graham, Superintendent, Auburn Correctional Facility. 561 U.S. 1039, 130 S. Ct. 3503,

177 L. Ed. 2d 1115,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 5263. June 28, 2010.
